---
source: crates/cosmon-cli/tests/help_goldens.rs
expression: stdout
---
Show help — all commands grouped, or detailed help for one command

Usage: cs help [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]

Arguments:
  [COMMAND]  Command to show help for (delegates to `cs <command> --help`)

Options:
      --config <PATH>  Path to configuration file
  -v, --verbose        Enable verbose output
      --json           Output in JSON format
  -h, --help           Print help

EXAMPLES:
  cs help                         # grouped command reference
  cs help tackle                  # detailed help for one command
  cs help guide                   # embedded operator handbook
  cs help charter                 # visual charter swatch
